{{zh-forms|alt=脈}}
Unclear. Reminiscent of {{och-l|脢|dorsal meat}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Alternatively, it may be of substrate origin. Compare ({{zh-ref|Deng, 1994}}):
* {{cog|map-pro|*SimaR||grease; oil; fat}} > {{cog|ami|simal}};
* {{cog|tai-pro|*manᴬ||grease; fat}} > {{cog|th|มัน}};
* {{cog|ms|gemuk||fat|pos=adjective}};
* {{cog|bnn|masmuh||fat|pos=adjective}};
* {{cog|huq||{{IPAfont|maʔ˥˧}}|fat|pos=adjective}}.

